<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Sana leh dangka haw a tatdawk ka hi puoi,
 Lei sum leh paiin ka thagau tan zolo;
 Kross thisan lul chuh ka hinna suongphum ahi,
 Ka hukdampa thihna chun ei hukdam tai.

[V2]
 Sana leh dangka a tat kei puoi,
 Dangka a tat ka hi puoi;
 Isu thisana tat ka hi zawi,
 Hehpih man simsen loh in.

[V3]
 2. Sana leh dangka haw a tatdawk ka hi puoi,
 Ka lunggil thiemloh a kichan zing laiin
 Kross thisan lul chuh ka hinna suongphum ahi,
 Ka hukdampa thihna maiin ei tan thei.

[V4]
 3. Sana leh dangka haw a tatdawk ka hi puoi,
 Thienthona dan thupiek chun ei dal laiin;
 Kross thisan lul chuh ka hinna suongphum ahi,
 Ka Hukdampa thihna'n lauhna a subei.

[V5]
 4. Sana leh dangka haw a tatdawk ka hi puoi,
 Ka van zawtna ding lampi a chawzo puoi;
 Kross thisan lul chuh ka hinna suongphum ahi,
 Ka hukdampa thihna chun ei tandawk tai.</lyrics>
<title>NOR SILVER NOR GOLD</title>
<hymn_number>449</hymn_number>
</song>